### Handy variables

### Volume and brightness steps
    set $volume_step 5
    set $brightness_step 2

### Swaylock timeout
    set $lock_timer 300
    set $black_screen_timer 60

### Wallpaper
    set $wallpaper "$HOME/Pictures/.wallpaper"
    set $lock_bg "$HOME/Pictures/.screensaver"

### Set a defalut file for the quick open of the org-agenda
    set $emacs_agenda "~/org/agenda/$(date '+%Y').org"
